//dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9999999956301053, \"rank\": 2.5359124544553616e-09, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This comes at a time when councils are already facing huge budget cuts.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Duncan Scott is now Scotland's most decorated Olympian after claiming his eighth medal - a silver in the men's 200 metres individual medley final on Friday.\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2570, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9999999956301053, \"rank\": 2.5359124544553616e-09, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 2616, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999855435818, \"rank\": 1.4456402070365172e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Glasgow-born swimmer is now ahead of Scotland's Sir Chris Hoy in terms of medals won.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2769, \"end\": 2777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9999999956301053, \"rank\": 2.5359124544553616e-09, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 2784, \"end\": 2793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2956, \"end\": 2969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3063836948376046e-15, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3063836948376046e-15, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"